---
title: Chinese Orange Chicken with Sesame Rice and Roasted Broccoli
description: Chinese Orange Chicken is a dish that has been adopted around the world. Tonight we are kicking the takeout box to the curb and making our own! This chopstick-worthy sesame rice bowl gets its umami edge with a punchy oyster sauce, sticky chicken and tender broccoli!
